     FMBDPL02 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAAMPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FQPRINT  O   F     132     OF     PRINTER
     E                    PRC        15  3               PROCESS
     E                    PRX        15  4               PROCESS
     I            DS
     I                                        1  45 PRC
     I                                        1   3 CKKO01
     I                                        4   6 CKKO02
     I                                        7   9 CKKO03
